Tonight, I point at some fields,

00:14.243 --> 00:17.082
Richard minces round a corner,

00:17.083 --> 00:19.883
and James describes
his ideal night in.

00:19.955 --> 00:23.131
Vomit and sputum,
and other bodily secretions.

