59:37.345 --> 59:40.384
A tractor.

59:40.385 --> 59:41.585
I didn't think of that.

59:44.745 --> 59:47.025
Land speed record cars!

59:48.585 --> 59:51.865
There's my bus! All right, mate?

59:57.545 --> 59:58.585
Ooh, the Eagle!

